headline: The Bull Case For lululemon athletica (LULU) Could Change Following New Training Line And Quality Concerns - Learn Why
summary: Earlier this month, lululemon athletica launched its Unrestricted Power™ training platform in North America, featuring the new PowerLu™ fabric and athlete-tested designs aimed at heavy lifting and high-intensity workouts. At the same time, the company is contending with renewed criticism over see-through leggings and leadership uncertainty, raising fresh questions about product quality control and brand direction.
